Scott Cash , 13News Now 9:51 p.m. EDT October 16, 2015 Oscar Smith vs Western Branch (Photo: WVEC Sports) 2 CONNECT 1 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
The streak lives on, or should we say survives. Thanks to a 4th quarter touchdown and a defensive stop Oscar Smith beat Western Branch 23-21. The win is the Tigers' 80th straight in the Southeastern District. Read or Share this story: http://on.wvec.com/1LyPXe7 TOP VIDEOS
